summary: This is a U.S. Customs and Border Protection travel manifest for a private flight arriving at KTEB (Teterboro Airport) on September 13, 2018. It lists Jeffrey Epstein and two other individuals as passengers/crew, showing their travel authorization statuses.

persons.name: Jeffrey Edward Epstein
persons.context: Listed as a passenger (PAX) on a private flight arriving at Teterboro Airport on September 13, 2018, with travel authorization status 'NOT REQUIRED'.

persons.name: David Neville Rodgers
persons.context: Listed as a crew member (CRW) on the same private flight as Jeffrey Epstein, with travel authorization status 'NOT REQUIRED'.

connections.description: Both were on the same private flight arriving at Teterboro Airport on September 13, 2018, with Epstein as a passenger and Rodgers as crew.

events.title: Private flight arrival at Teterboro
events.description: A private flight (tail number N120JE) arrived at KTEB (Teterboro Airport) at 17:55 local time, carrying Jeffrey Epstein and others.

keyFacts: Jeffrey Epstein traveled on a private flight (tail number N120JE) that arrived at Teterboro Airport (KTEB) on September 13, 2018.
David Neville Rodgers was listed as a crew member on the same flight.
Both Epstein and Rodgers had travel authorization status 'NOT REQUIRED' for this entry into the United States.
